            <title><![CDATA[中国光大集团原董事长李晓鹏被查]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/05/y_2.jpeg?VersionId=floGIgUgv2aQS_qMvAYqLSoTEH3GfeUK&amp;itok=nNtxZNca" title="中国光大集团股份公司原党委书记、董事长李晓鹏被查。（互联网）" alt="中国光大集团股份公司原党委书记、董事长李晓鹏被查。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/05/y_2.jpeg?VersionId=floGIgUgv2aQS_qMvAYqLSoTEH3GfeUK&amp;itok=nNtxZNca" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
